<h3>Wed</h3>
<p>10.03.07</p>
<a href="/tim"><img src="/images/people/photo_tim_s.jpg" width="57" alt="Tim O'Reilly" /></a>
<p><a href="/tim">Tim O'Reilly</a></p>
