<p>The 'military intelligence' sense of the word is actually roughly the same as the 'business intelligence' sense, and probably a few other variants that escape me right now.</p>

<p>But all of those senses of the word 'intelligence' are rather different from the separate 'IQ' sense of the word.</p>
